gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Suns 110, Grizzlies 89
gameRecap.excerpt: The Suns defeated the Grizzlies, 110-89 as they won their sixth consecutive game. Devin Booker led the Suns with a season high 40 points (15-21 FG, 3-4 3PT), five rebounds, four assists, and four steals as Eric Gordon totaled 20 points. Santi Aldama led Memphis with 21 points and five rebounds as Derrick Rose went 8-9 FG for 17 points. The Suns improve to 10-6 in the regular season and 3-1 in West A play as the Grizzlies move to 3-12 and 0-4.
